youth and will continue its commitment through resource
allocation, coordination and promotion efforts," the Chief
Executive said.
</P>
<P>
Tung pointed out that with Hong Kong's reunification with the
motherland, the SAR government had the responsibility to
enhance young people's sense of belonging to the country, and
increase their knowledge of the motherland.
</P>
<P>
The four organizations hold joint meetings regularly to discuss
how they can improve young people's understanding of the society
and culture, increase their civic awareness and help them
establish a positive value standard. 
</P>
</TEXT>
