<HEADLINE> Bosnich Named Oceania's Keeper of Century </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, August 25 (Xinhua) -- Australia's Mark Bosnich was
on Tuesday named Oceania's "Goalkeeper of the Century".
</P>
<P>
The Aston Villa soccer player was selected in a poll by the
International Federation of Football History and Statistics.
</P>
<P>
He received 53 votes from a group of sports statisticians and
journalists, far ahead of 21 by runner-up Frank van Hattum of New
Zealand. 
</P>
