<HEADLINE> Vietnam Intensifies Anti-Drug Fight </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, August 25 (Xinhua) -- The Vietnamese police in the
capital city of Hanoi arrested 1,886 people for their involvement
in more than 900 cases of drug smuggling, trafficking, stockpiling
and selling and organizing illegal drug use in the first seven
months of this year, an official report said Tuesday.
