<HEADLINE> Jiang Zemin Meets AP Delegation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 25 (Xinhua)-- Chinese President Jiang Zemin is
meeting here this morning with a delegation of the Board of
Directors of the Associated Press of the United States.
</P>
<P>
AT press time the meeting is still going on.
</P>
<P>
Jiang has a friendly talk with the delegation and also answers
their questions concerning the future of Sino-U.S. relations and
China's economic and social development.
</P>
<P>
The delegation, co-headed by Donald E Newhouse, Chairman of AP,
and Louis Donald Boccardi, its President and Chief Executive
Officer, arrived in Beijing on Sunday at the invitation of Xinhua
News Agency.
</P>
<P>
The delegation will also visit Xi'an, Shanghai, Guilin and Hong
Kong. 
</P>
